"turn to the right into the highway to Barnet, &c. There go straight across to a field-gate, with the stile of a field- })ath beside it; and take this path, keeping to the extreme eft track where two others branch off, till you come out into a road. There turn to the right for a full half-mile, till you come to the cross-roads at the centre of the old hamlet of Colney Hatch, with the Orange-tree tavern on your left. Here take the left-hand road (to Whetstone"